sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User (Flutter)
  participant S3 as S3 (presigned)
  participant API as FastAPI
  participant MW as Middleware<br/>(Auth/RateLimit)
  participant LG as LangGraphCoach
  participant VS as VisionService
  participant GEM as Gemini API
  participant RAG as RAG (Chroma)
  participant DB as Supabase PG
  participant FCM as FCM/APNs

  Note over U,API: Case A — Chat with food image
  U->>S3: PUT presigned (image)
  S3-->>U: 200
  U->>API: POST /chat/messages {text, media_url}
  API->>MW: verify JWT + rate limit
  MW-->>API: user_id
  API->>LG: dispatch(message, media)
  LG->>VS: classify_media_content(url)
  VS->>GEM: vision classify (T=0.1)
  GEM-->>VS: food_plate
  VS-->>LG: media_content_type
  LG->>LG: route → Nutrition Agent
  LG->>RAG: retrieve saved foods + nutrition ctx
  RAG-->>LG: vectors
  LG->>GEM: agent LLM (bind_tools)
  GEM-->>LG: tool_call: analyze_food_image
  LG->>GEM: vision tool call
  GEM-->>LG: parsed foods + macros
  LG->>DB: INSERT food_log rows
  LG->>GEM: response_after_tools
  GEM-->>LG: final message + action_data
  LG-->>API: stream SSE
  API-->>U: SSE tokens + action_data
  U->>U: render + _handleSettingChange

  Note over U,API: Case B — Offline workout generation
  U->>U: connectivity lost (1.5s debounce)
  U->>U: WorkoutGenerationOrchestrator
  alt pre-cached server workouts exist
    U->>U: load from Drift
  else rule-based path
    U->>U: templates + progressive_overload
  else on-device AI
    U->>U: flutter_gemma (Gemma 1B/4B)
  end
  U-->>U: render workout (no fallback between modes)

  Note over API,FCM: Case C — Scheduled nudge (cron)
  API->>DB: SELECT users in local-time window
  loop per user (user-local TZ)
    API->>API: compose by time-of-day + schedule
    API->>FCM: send push
    API->>DB: log notification
  end
